#: .\portfolioapp\templates\index.html:88
msgid "stroy desc"
msgstr ""
" Hello, I am Hamza ,I studied Intelligent Computer System Engineering at "
"Algiers 1, one of Algeria's top universities. During my studies, I worked on "
"several internships, which helped me build a solid foundation in system "
"design and engineering. Now that I've got a couple of years of work "
"experience, I'm involved in some big e-learning projects where we use "
"artificial intelligence to make learning more personalized and engaging. On "
"the side, I also create content about technology, programming, and AI. I "
"write blog posts, make videos, and generally try to share what I know with "
"others. I enjoy breaking down complicated tech concepts and making them "
"easier to understand. I think technology can make a huge impact on people's "
"lives, and I'm glad I can contribute to that."

